telecomunicaciones Visuales ay 
Universidad Politecnica de Madrid UPM


This Repository contains two files: 



1. encoder_top.v:   this file is intended to connect DUT internal components

2. encoder_top_tb.v: this file contains code to connet all components required for simulation

 To run:

Integrate the testbench model in your hardware IDE 
add your code and lunch simulation


Dependencies: unknown

Any question, please contact me at gic@gatv.ssr.upm.es

Enjoy it!



